          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1617708319476-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the <strong>basa fillets</strong> dry with kitchen paper and cut each fillet in half on a diagonal</p><p>Season the<strong> basa</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and sprinkle both sides with <strong>flour</strong> until fully coated, then tap off any excess</p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1617708380397-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1617708380397-x400.jpg",
