            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1617708399451-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the reserved pot, cover them with<strong> boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through, then drain and return to the pot with a knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Mash the peas until they come together nicely – these are your <strong>mushy peas</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
